summary: Now you can become the best assassin with this full armor set that also includes a sword. This mod was inspired from Corvo\'s gear from Dishonored, and is a completely new armor mesh made from scratch.
descriptionHtml:
Now you can become the best assassin with this full armor set that also includes a sword that all once belonged to the infamous \'Royal Assassin\'. This mod was inspired from Corvo\'s gear from Dishonored, and is a completely new armor mesh made from scratch. Everything can be found inside a cell in the Solitude prison, beside the Royal Assassin\'s skeleton. Enjoy!

Ideas? Suggestions? You can always message me your requests, suggestions, or even join the RTG modding team!
author: Rodger Phillips
